        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">There was no data available on process emissions to air for the sodium nitrite production. As approximation the air emissions occurring from the purge vent, the distillation vent and fugitive emission sources were estimated to 0.2% of the input of nitrogen dioxide and nitrogen monoxide. The remaining amount of nitrogen dioxide and nitrogen monoxide is considered to be reduced to nitrogen.</comment>
